  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Queen Slayer</i> is a tightly focused, streamlined turn-based roguelike RPG you can complete in 2–3 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a party of 4 from 15 unique mercenaries and take on 8 corrupted queens in intense boss battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No grinding, no filler—every fight is a boss fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/558c66a67251b36d20bb418f771d3b51.poster.avif?t=1770094622\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/558c66a67251b36d20bb418f771d3b51.webm?t=1770094622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/558c66a67251b36d20bb418f771d3b51.mp4?t=1770094622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/d0fc153501f5ba5be5ee025ff5ecfbb3.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short and intense combat loop – complete the game in just 2–3 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss-focused structure – every battle leads straight to one of the 8 corrupted queens</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 mercenaries, 4-slot party – encourages different strategies every run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growth & choice – simple but meaningful progression system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve 100% completion in a single session<br>→ All achievements tied to defeating 8 queens can be completed in one playthrough</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/f4047af1ec671cfec7beae6c1b474072.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A different choice, a new journey every time</strong><br>Even within a short playtime, the variety of mercenary combinations and strategic shifts offer fresh combat experiences every run.<br>Quick to finish, but always tempting to restart for another challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world has been consumed by corrupted queens.<br>Covered in poison, ice, blood, and iron, each queen overwhelms with her own distinct style and visual identity.<br>In this dark and intense fantasy, every turn and every decision reshapes the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/06fc1f7bce03c30bea2e9dc91f58b833.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Queen Slayer</i> offers a small yet meaningful challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the charm of turn-based combat and dark fantasy, and discover your own unique strategy.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Queen Slayer</i> is a tightly focused, streamlined turn-based roguelike RPG you can complete in 2–3 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a party of 4 from 15 unique mercenaries and take on 8 corrupted queens in intense boss battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No grinding, no filler—every fight is a boss fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/558c66a67251b36d20bb418f771d3b51.poster.avif?t=1770094622\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/558c66a67251b36d20bb418f771d3b51.webm?t=1770094622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/558c66a67251b36d20bb418f771d3b51.mp4?t=1770094622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/d0fc153501f5ba5be5ee025ff5ecfbb3.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short and intense combat loop – complete the game in just 2–3 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss-focused structure – every battle leads straight to one of the 8 corrupted queens</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 mercenaries, 4-slot party – encourages different strategies every run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growth & choice – simple but meaningful progression system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve 100% completion in a single session<br>→ All achievements tied to defeating 8 queens can be completed in one playthrough</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/f4047af1ec671cfec7beae6c1b474072.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A different choice, a new journey every time</strong><br>Even within a short playtime, the variety of mercenary combinations and strategic shifts offer fresh combat experiences every run.<br>Quick to finish, but always tempting to restart for another challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world has been consumed by corrupted queens.<br>Covered in poison, ice, blood, and iron, each queen overwhelms with her own distinct style and visual identity.<br>In this dark and intense fantasy, every turn and every decision reshapes the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/06fc1f7bce03c30bea2e9dc91f58b833.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Queen Slayer</i> offers a small yet meaningful challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the charm of turn-based combat and dark fantasy, and discover your own unique strategy.</p>",
